'''變異中心'''（center of diversity）指的是一個[[種|種]]或[[屬_(生物)|屬]]的生物[[遺傳變異|基因高度變異]]的地區，變異中心同時也很可能是[[起源中心|起源中心]]。<ref name=aps>{{cite web|title=Knowledge Test Questions and Answers for Discussion|publisher=The American Phytopathological Society|url=http://www.apsnet.org/education/InstructorCommunication/Restricted/Advanced/discussion/population_genetics.html|accessdate=2008-12-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090514224024/http://www.apsnet.org/education/InstructorCommunication/Restricted/Advanced/discussion/population_genetics.html|archivedate=2009-05-14}}</ref><ref name=osu>{{cite web|title=Centers of Diversity, Crop Adaptation|publisher=[[Oregon_State_University|Oregon State University]]|url=http://oregonstate.edu/instruct/css/330/two/|accessdate=2008-12-18|archive-date=2008-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080707074537/http://oregonstate.edu/instruct/css/330/two/|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 這個術語是由前蘇聯科學家[[尼古拉·伊萬諾維奇·瓦維洛夫|尼古拉·伊萬諾維奇·瓦維洛夫]]和美國科學家[[傑克·哈倫|傑克·哈倫]]創造出來的，<ref name=ac>{{cite book|author=George Acquaah|title=Principles of plant genetics and breeding|year=2006|publisher=[[Blackwell_Publishing|Blackwell Publishing]]|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Xrwvjo2myTMC&pg=PA19&dq=%22center+of+diversity%22+vavilov+concept&ei=kSRISb6sDZCqkATO-9jwDw|isbn=978-1-4051-3646-4|access-date=2014-04-20|archive-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705020321/http://books.google.com/books?id=Xrwvjo2myTMC&pg=PA19&dq=%22center+of+diversity%22+vavilov+concept&ei=kSRISb6sDZCqkATO-9jwDw|dead-url=no}}</ref> 瓦維洛夫在1926年發表的研究《種植植物起源研究》中列出了十個變異中心：
*1 - [[中國|中國]]：[[生菜|生菜]]、[[大黃|大黃]]、[[大豆|大豆]]和[[蕪菁|蕪菁]]
*2 - [[印度|印度]]：[[黃瓜|黃瓜]]、[[大米|大米]]、[[芒果|芒果]]和亞洲[[棉花|棉花]]
*2a - [[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]]：[[香蕉|香蕉]]、[[椰子|椰子]]和[[大米|大米]]
*3 - [[中亞|中亞]]（北印度、阿富汗和土庫曼斯坦）：[[扁桃樹|扁桃樹]]、[[蘋果|蘋果]]、[[亞麻|亞麻]]和[[兵豆|兵豆]]
*4 - [[近東|近東]]：[[苜蓿|苜蓿]]、[[捲心菜|捲心菜]]和[[黑麥|黑麥]]
*5 - [[地中海|地中海]]沿海：[[薺菜|薺菜]]、[[鷹嘴豆|鷹嘴豆]]和[[杜蘭小麥|杜蘭小麥]]
*6 - [[埃塞俄比亞|埃塞俄比亞]]：[[咖啡|咖啡]]、[[高粱|高粱]]和[[珍珠粟|珍珠粟]]
*7 - [[墨西哥|墨西哥]]南部和[[中美洲|中美洲]]：[[玉米|玉米]]、[[利馬豆|利馬豆]]、[[木瓜|木瓜]]和[[陸地棉|陸地棉]]
*8 - [[南美洲|南美洲]]西北部（[[玻利維亞|玻利維亞]]、[[厄瓜多爾|厄瓜多爾]]和[[秘魯|秘魯]]）：[[馬鈴薯|馬鈴薯]]、[[西紅柿|西紅柿]]和[[埃及棉|埃及棉]]
*8a - [[智利|智利]]的諸島：馬鈴薯<ref name=ac/>

